Planned strikes by ground workers
and cabin crew at Iberia,  IAG (IAG) ’s Spanish airline, may make the
company’s situation “unmanageable,” according to Iberia Chief
Executive Officer Rafael Sanchez-Lozano,  Cinco Dias  reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
